Subject:Re: [Flexradio] "SPEC" mode ??
Dan,

It is documented somewhere, like the Owner's Manual. ;-)

It is the SPECtrum mode.  It displays a 0Hz IF spectrum of the entire 
sampled bandwidth without demodulation.  So if you are sampling at 96 
KHz you will see +/- 48 KHz of spectrum

Tim Ellison
